That’s why I’m excited to share a breakthrough: Melasyl, a new ingredient in the fight against dark spots!

I’ve been using the L’Oréal Paris Glycolic Bright Serum powered by Melasyl with a new ingredient and pairing it with the Invisible Resist Sunscreen—a duo that not only treats existing dark spots but also prevents new ones from forming by shielding your skin from harmful UV rays.

Sun protection + targeted treatment = visible results!
